Module kivakit.core.resource
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.resource.reading

Class ResourceReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.resource.reading.ResourceReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StringSource, Source<java.lang.String>
    public class ResourceReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements StringSource
    Resource reader provides a variety of convenient ways of reading a resource, including as bytes (bytes()), as a single string (string()), as lines (linesAsStringList()), and as objects (addObjectsTo(Collection, Converter, ProgressReporter) and objects(Converter, ProgressReporter)).
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
